TITLE: Episode 85 - The Spiciest Welfare with the Biting the Bullet Boys
DESCRIPTION: This week, Maddie and Jessie talk to the boys from Biting the Bullet, Luke and Typo. Both former Marines with the goal of fighting the war machine from their unique position as anti-war vets, the boys bring a much needed perspective when it comes to the military, the spiciest welfare of all.
